snippet.title: Hearts of Iron IV: Man the Guns - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Man the Guns, the latest expansion for Hearts of Iron IV, focuses on Naval Warfare and adds new mechanics for playing democratic nations, including new alternate history paths. Man the Guns will be available on February 28th 2019.
